  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\nThe loading spinner appears for a moment on profile pictures when performing actions such as:\r\n- adding/removing a contact\r\n- mute/unmute\r\n- adding a nickname\r\n- changing the online status visibility in own profile\r\n- etc\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nProfile picture doesn't blink\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/183041160-ec8fc179-1d0d-436a-8576-c6c75dd198ac.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Open Status\r\n2. Open profile of some user\r\n3. Add to contacts, mute\r\n4. Navigate to own profile > change the online status\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 5/08\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n",
